tarlink%20access.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThere's%20no%20clear%20sign%20of%20that%20happening%20yet%2C%20but%20Eutelsat%20said%20it's%20in%20talks%20with%20the%20EU.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFrench%20satellite%20provider%20Eutelsat's%20shares%20tripled%20over%20the%20last%20two%20days%20amid%20concerns%20that%20Ukraine's%20access%20to%20Starlink%20may%20be%20under%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEutelsat%20shares%20on%20the%20Paris%20exchange%20surged%2068%25%20on%20Monday%20before%20jumping%20another%20123%25%20the%20next%20morning%20to%20%244.77.%20Prices%20tapered%20off%20at%20%243.79%20at%20market%20close%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20leap%20comes%20as%20the%20US%20suspended%20aid%20to%20Ukraine%20on%20Monday%2C%20prompting%20fears%20of%20disruptions%20to%20capabilities%20like%20advanced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzelenskyy-advisor-patriots-weapon-concern-over-trump-aid-cuts-ukraine-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20air%20defenses%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20internet%20access%20on%20the%20battlefield.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarlink%2C%20owned%20by%20Elon%20Musk's%20SpaceX%2C%20has%20been%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fofficials-worry-about-ukraines-reliance-on-elon-musks-starlink-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evital%20internet%20provider%20for%20Ukraine's%20military%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20loss%20of%20its%20services%20would%20be%20a%20severe%20blow%20to%20Kyiv's%20communications%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-drones-are-causing-mayhem-in-the-ukraine-war-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrone%20operations%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20key%20for%20Eutelsat%2C%20which%20merged%20with%20a%20UK-based%20Starlink%20competitor%2C%20OneWeb%2C%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20satellite%20firm%20has%20come%20to%20the%20fore%20as%20European%20leaders%20say%20they're%20bolstering%20defense%20spending%20while%20raising%20the%20possibility%20that%20they%20could%20seek%20to%20fill%20any%20gaps%20in%20Ukraine's%20internet%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20its%20share%20price%20rose%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20company%20told%20Reuters%20it%20was%20discussing%20with%20the%20European%20Union%20how%20it%20might%20contribute%20to%20Ukraine's%20internet%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20told%20The%20Financial%20Times%20it%20had%20equipment%20ready%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bdeployed%20swiftly%20in%20Ukraine%20to%20connect%20the%20most%20critical%20missions%20and%20infrastructures.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20jump%20this%20week%2C%20Eutelstat's%20shares%20are%20still%20far%20below%20its%20past%20highs.%20Its%20stock%20reached%20about%20%2433%20in%20mid-2015%20and%20has%20steadily%20declined%20in%20the%20last%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEutelsat%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228a6cc428-5223-4c47-a48d-5d476fb0e06c%5C%22%3ENo%20official%20sign%20yet%20that%20Starlink%20will%20disappear%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20it's%20unclear%20whether%20Ukraine's%20Starlink%20access%20is%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%2C%20a%20close%20ally%20of%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20denied%20a%20Reuters%20report%20from%20late%20February%20that%20said%20US%20officials%20discussed%20cutting%20off%20Starlink%20from%20Kyiv%20if%20it%20rejected%20a%20minerals%20deal%20with%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20the%20US%20partially%20pays%20for%20Ukraine's%20Starlink%20subscription%2C%20European%20countries%20also%20fund%20many%20terminals.%20Poland%2C%20which%20pays%20for%20about%20half%20of%20Ukraine's%20Starlink%20terminals%2C%20said%20it%20would%20continue%20to%20fund%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20OneWeb%2C%20Eutelsat%20is%20also%20already%20providing%20some%20satellite%20services%20to%20Ukraine's%20governments%20and%20institutions%2C%20but%20it%20only%20has%20about%20one-tenth%20of%20Starlink's%20satellites.%20Its%20constellation%20has%20fewer%20than%20700%20satellites%2C%20while%20Starlink%20runs%20over%207%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20European%20company%20operates%2035%20Geo%20satellites%2C%20which%20orbit%20at%2021%2C000%20miles%20above%20Earth%2C%20and%20about%20630%20low-earth%20orbit%20satellites%2C%20which%20orbit%20at%20about%20750%20miles%20above%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20European%20Commission%20spokesperson%20Thomas%20Regnier%20told%20reporters%20regional%20leaders%20were%20considering%20giving%20Ukraine%20access%20to%20GovSatCom%20as%20an%20alternative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20system%20is%20a%20shared%20network%20of%20satellites%20already%20owned%20by%20European%20member%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEutelsat's%20momentary%20stock%20boost%20also%20comes%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Feuropean-defense-stocks-ukraine-war-rheinmetall-bae-systems-leonardo-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEuropean%20defense%20manufacturing%20shares%20surged%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20the%20recent%20strain%20on%20US%20relations%20with%20its%20traditional%20allies%20and%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUrsula%20von%20der%20Leyen%2C%20president%20of%20the%20European%20Commission%2C%20announced%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20European%20leaders%20would%20push%20to%20allocate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feurope-boosting-defense-spending-ukraine-rearm-plan-trump-zelenskyy-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E800%20billion%20euros%2C%20or%20about%20%24840%20billion%2C%20to%20their%20defense%20spending%3C%2Fa%3E%20collectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarlink-competitor-eutelsat-oneweb-trump-us-aid-ukraine-internet-satellite-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741155425000%2C%22visual%22%3A%