20Rao%2C%20Kannada%20Actor%20Arrested%20On%20Gold%20Smuggling%20Charges%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKannada%20actor%20Ranya%20Rao%20was%20arrested%20at%20Bengaluru's%20Kempegowda%20International%20Airport%20after%2014.8%20kilograms%20of%20gold%20was%20allegedly%20found%20in%20her%20possession.%20She%20was%20produced%20before%20a%20judge%20on%20Tuesday%20evening%20and%20was%20remanded%20to%2014-day%20judicial%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20is%20all%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20her%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERao%20hails%20from%20Karnataka's%20Chikamagaluru.%20She%20completed%20an%20engineering%20degree%20from%20Dayanad%20Sagar%20College%20of%20Engineering%20in%20Bangalore.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERao%20made%20her%20film%20debut%20in%202014%20opposite%20Kannada%20superstar%20Sudeep%20in%20'Maanikya'%20(2014).%20A%20remake%20of%202013%20Telugu%20film%20Mirchi%2C%20Maanikya%20portrays%20Rao%20as%20Manasa%2C%20a%20woman%20from%20an%20influential%20family%20who%20becomes%20Sudeep's%20love%20interest.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EShe%20has%20also%20appeared%20in%20Tamil%20film%20Wagah%20(2016)%20opposite%20Vikram%20Prabhu.%20Ranya%20plays%20Prabhu's%20love%20interest%20in%20the%20film%2C%20which%20shows%20an%20Indian%20soldier%20escorting%20her%20back%20home%20to%20Pakistan%20after%20riots%20break%20out%20in%20India.%20is%20caught%20in%20a%20fix%20when%20riots%20break%20out%20in%20Kashmir%20and%20amidst%20all%20the%20protest%20against%20the%20Pakistani%20residents%20there%2C%20he%20has%20to%20take%20his%20lover%20back%20to%20her%20home%2C%20in%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20the%20Kannada%20comedy%20film%20Pataki%20(2017)%2C%20she%20portrays%20Sangeetha%2C%20a%20journalist%20and%20the%20love%20interest%20of%20actor%20Ganesh's%20character.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EShe%20claims%20to%20be%20the%20stepdaughter%20of%20IPS%20officer%20and%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20(Police%20Housing%20Corporation)%20Ramachandra%20Rao.%3C%2F