and%20PSU%20Bank%20sectors%20in%20early%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20around%209.31%20am%2C%20Sensex%20was%20trading%20358.34%20points%20or%200.49%20per%20cent%20up%20at%2073%2C348.27%20while%20the%20Nifty%20added%20106.40%20points%20or%200.48%20per%20cent%20at%2022%2C189.05.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENifty%20Bank%20was%20up%20147.80%20points%20or%200.31%20per%20cent%20at%2048%2C393.%20The%20Nifty%20Midcap%20100%20index%20was%20trading%20at%2048%2C337.15%20after%20adding%20329.30%20points%20or%200.69%20per%20cent.%20Nifty%20Smallcap%20100%20index%20was%20at%2014%2C909.40%20after%20rising%20146.80%20points%20or%200.99%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20experts%2C%20markets%20could%20see%20a%20subdued%20opening%20tracking%20overnight%20weakness%20in%20US%20markets%2C%20but%20optimism%20in%20other%20Asian%20indices%20may%20aid%20sentiment%20after%20benchmark%20Nifty%20ended%20in%20red%20for%20the%2010th%20day%20in%20a%20row%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20market%20is%20dealing%20with%20the%20pessimism%20of%20the%20likely%20impact%20of%20Trump's%20reciprocating%20tariff%20policy%20amidst%20escalating%20trade%20tensions%20and%20growing%20signs%20of%20an%20economic%20slowdown%20and%20sticky%20US%20inflation%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Prashanth%20Tapse%2C%20Sr%20VP%20Research%20Analyst%20at%20Mehta%20Equities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTechnically%2C%20in%20case%20Nifty%20gives%20up%2022%2C000%20on%20a%20closing%20basis%2C%20then%20the%20next%20big%20support%20will%20come%20at%2021%2C281%20mark%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20ongoing%20volatility%2C%20traders%20are%20advised%20to%20exercise%20caution%2C%20implement%20strict%20stop-loss%20strategies%2C%20and%20avoid%20carrying%20overnight%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20the%20Sensex%20pack%2C%20HCL%20Tech%2C%20M%26amp%3BM%2C%20PowerGrid%2C%20Tech%20Mahindra%2C%20Zomato%2C%20Tata%20Steel%2C%20Tata%20Motors%20and%20ICICI%20Bank%20were%20the%20t