%20be%20based%20on%20merit%20and%20the%20country%20%26quot%3Bwill%20no%20longer%20be%20woke%26quot%3B%2C%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20told%20a%20joint%20session%20of%20Congress%20today%2C%20as%20he%20stressed%20that%20his%20administration%20had%20ended%20the%20%26quot%3Btyranny%26quot%3B%20of%20diversity%20and%20inclusion%20programmes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20his%20first%20address%20to%20Congress%20since%20the%20thumping%20win%20in%20the%20November%20election%20and%20came%20four%20years%20after%20his%20supporters%20stormed%20the%20Capitol%20building%20to%20protest%20the%202020%20election%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EListing%20multiple%20diversity%20programmes%20funded%20by%20the%20US%20in%20several%20parts%20of%20the%20world%20and%20launching%20a%20no-holds-barred%20attack%20on%20the%20Joe%20Biden%20regime%2C%20Trump%20said%20the%20country%20had%20suffered%20its%20worst%20inflation%20in%2048%20years%20and%20his%20top%20priority%20was%20to%20rescue%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20two%20months%20in%20the%20top%20post%2C%20the%2078-year-old%20said%20he%20is%20%26quot%3Bjust%20getting%20started%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20%26quot%3BAmerica%20is%20back%26quot%3B.%C2%A0As%20he%20spoke%2C%20several%20Democrats%20waved%20placards%20that%20read%20%26quot%3Bfalse%26quot%3B.%20Congressman%20Al%20Green%20was%20asked%20to%20leave%20the%20gathering%20after%20heckled%20and%20shook%20his%20walking%20stick%20at%20the%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20accomplished%20more%20in%2043%20days%20than%20most%20administrations%20accomplish%20in%20four%20years%20or%20eight%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20American%20Dream%20is%20surging%20--%20bigger%20and%20better%20than%20ever%20before.%20The%20American%20Dream%20is%20unstoppable%2C%20and%20our%20country%20is%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20a%20comeback%20the%20likes%20of%20which%20the%20world%20has%20never%20witnessed%2C%20and%20perhaps%20will%20never%20witness%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20country%20will%20be%20woke%20no%20longer.%20We%20believe%20that%20whether%20you%20are%20a%20doctor%2C%20an%20accountant%2C%20a%20lawyer%20or%20(an)%20air%20traffic%20controller%2C%20you%20should%20be%20hired%20and%20promoted%20based%20on%20skills%20and%20competence%2C%20not%20race%20or%20gender%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20in%20an%20all-out%20attack%20against%20wokeism.%20%26quot%3BWokeness%20is%20trouble%2C%20wokeness%20is%20bad%2C%20it's%20gone%20and%20we%20feel%20so%20much%20better%20for%20it%2C%20don't%20we%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20was%20working%20tirelessly%20to%20end%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20and%20spoke%20at%20length%20about%20how%20his%20administration%20was%20working%20to%20curb%20illegal%20immigration%20into%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20address%2C%20Trump%20praised%20his%20advisor%20and%20billionaire%20Elon%20Musk%20for%20his%20work%20leading%20the%20Department%20of%20Government%20Efficiency%2C%20which%20has%20been%20tasked%20with%20trimming%20the%20federal%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThank%20you%20Elon%2C%20he's%20working%20very%20hard%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20as%20Musk%20stood%20up%20in%20the%20gallery%20to%20applause%20from%20Republican%20lawmakers.%20%26quot%3BThank%20you%20very%20much%2C%20we%20appreciate%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20tariff%20war%20his%20administration%20has%20launched%20and%20referred%20to%20India%20in%20this%20connection.%20%26quot%3BOther%20countries%20have%20used%20tariffs%20against%20us%20for%20decades%20now.%20On%20an%20average%2C%20many%20nations...%20India%2C%20Mexico%20and%20Canada%2C%20they%20charge%20us%20tremendously%20higher%20tariffs%20than%20we%20charge%20them.%20India%20charges%20us%20auto%20tariffs%20higher%20than%20100%20per%20cent...%20this%20is%20happening%20by%20friend%20and%20foe.%20This%20situation%20is%20not%20fair%20to%20the%20US.%20So%20from%20Apri