20to%20praise%20the%20skipper%20for%20setting%20the%20right%20tempo%20from%20the%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Gambhir%20didn't%20share%20much%20light%20on%20Rohit's%20international%20future%2C%20he%20did%20confirm%20that%20it's%20the%20Hitman's%20'impact'%20with%20which%20he%20is%20evaluated%20and%20not%20his%20'numbers'.%20While%20the%20head%20coach's%20refusal%20to%20confirm%20Rohit's%20future%20ahead%20of%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20final%20is%20understood%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20completely%20dodged%20the%20question%20could%20hint%20that%20something%20is%20already%20being%20planned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReporter%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BTell%20me%20about%20Rohit%2C%20the%20form%20he's%20in%2C%20how%20much%20cricket%20do%20you%20think%20he'll%20still%20play%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%2C%20the%20final%20of%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20is%20now%20coming%20up.%20What%20can%20I%20say%20before%20that%3F%20If%20your%20captain%20bats%20with%20such%20a%20tempo%2C%20it%20just%20gives%20a%20very%20good%20signal%20to%20the%20dressing%20room%20that%20we%20want%20to%20be%20absolutely%20fearless%20and%20courageous.%20You%20evaluate%20from%20the%20runs%3B%20we%20evaluate%20from%20the%20impact.%20That's%20the%20difference.%20You%20evaluate%20from%20the%20stats%3B%20we%20evaluate%20from%20the%20impact.%20As%20journalists%2C%20as%20experts%2C%20you%20only%20look%20at%20numbers%2C%20averages.%20But%20as%20a%20coach%2C%20as%20a%20team%2C%20we%20don't%20look%20at%20numbers%20or%20averages.%20If%20the%20captain%20puts%20up%20his%20hand%20first%2C%20then%20there%20is%20nothing%20better%20than%20that%20for%20the%20dressing%20room%2C%26quot%3B%20Gambhir%20said%20in%20the%20post-match%20press%20conference.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EGambhir%20on%20Rohit%20Future%20Fabulous%20answer%20gazab%20jawab%20diya%20hai%20hum%20impact%20se%20judge%20karte%20naki%20averages%20se%20and%20yes%20Rohit%20will%20play%20Wc%202027%20well%20said%20Gautam%20(Courtesy%20ICC)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FINDvAUS%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23INDvAUS%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FCCODXUe6IO%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FCCODXUe6IO%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Imsajal45%20(%40Sajalsinha0264)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSajalsinha0264%2Fstatus%2F1896981577462329349%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%204%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20match%20against%20Australia%2C%20Rohit%20shattered%20a%20massive%20record%20and%20etched%20his%20name%20in%20the%20record%20books%20by%20becoming%20the%20first%20captain%20in%20the%20history%20of%20cricket%20to%20reach%20the%20finals%20of%20all%20ICC%20tournaments.%20India's%20momentous%20triumph%20over%20Australia%20in%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20semi-final%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20made%20India%20the%20first%20side%20to%20reach%20the%20fifth%20Champions%20Trophy%20final%2C%20no%20other%20team%20has%20reached%20more%20than%20three.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20Rohit%20took%20over%20full-time%20captaincy%20in%20February%202022%2C%20India%20has%20toppled%20several%20records.%20In%20a%20span%20of%20three%20years%2C%20India%20has%20entered%20the%20finals%20of%20every%20ICC%20tournament%2C%20making%20him%20the%20first%20skipper%20to%20achieve%20the%20feat.%20He%20has%20reached%20the%20finals%20of%20ICC%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%2C%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%2C%20ICC%20World%20Test%20Championship%202023%20and%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20having%20won%20the%20T20%20WC%202024%20out%20of%20these.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20four%20matches%20in%20the%20tournament%20so%20far%2C%20Rohit%20has%20not%20failed%20to%20deliver%20those%20crucial%20runs%20in%20the%20powerplay%20and%20has%20continued%20playing%20the%20role%20of