22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F118721764.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESecretary%20of%20Veterans%20Affairs%20Doug%20Collins%20will%20be%20the%20designated%20survivor%20for%20President%20Trump's%202025%20address%20to%20Congress%2C%20ensuring%20government%20continuity%20in%20case%20of%20an%20emergency.%20This%20tradition%20began%20in%20the%201950s%20during%20the%20Cold%20War.%20Past%20survivors%20describe%20a%20secure%20experience%20with%20military%20supervision.%20Recent%20designations%20include%20Education%20Secretary%20Miguel%20Cardona%20in%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrumps-2025-joint-address-to-congress-who-is-this-years-designated-survivor-and-what-it-means-doug-collins%2Farticleshow%2F118721764.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrumps-2025-joint-address-to-congress-who-is-this-years-designated-survivor-and-what-it-means-doug-collins%2Famp_articleshow%2F118721764.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrumps-2025-joint-address-to-congress-who-is-this-years-designated-survivor-and-what-it-means-doug-collins%2Famp_articleshow%2F118721764.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rohit%20Scripts%20Never-Seen-Before%20Record%20In%20ICC%20Events%2C%20Surpasses%20Dhoni%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERohit%20Sharma%20went%20on%20to%20script%20history%20once%20again%20as%20a%20skipper%20of%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team.%20The%20Hitman%20etched%20his%20name%20in%20the%20record%20books%20by%20becoming%20the%20first%20captain%20in%20the%20history%20of%20cricket%20to%20reach%20the%20finals%20of%20all%20four%20ICC%20tournaments.%20Former%20India%20captain%20MS%20Dhoni%20had%20managed%20to%20earn%20India%20trophies%20at%20three%20ICC%20events%20--%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20and%20Champions%20Trophy%20by%20helping%20India%20win%20three%20elusive%20finals%20in%202007%2C%202011%20and%202013%20respectively.%20But%2C%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20hadn't%20started%20before%20Dhoni%20retired%20from%20the%20longest%20format%20of%20the%20game.%20Virat%20Kohli%20had%20become%20the%20first%20captain%20to%20take%20India%20to%20the%20WTC%20final.%20However%2C%20Rohit%20has%20now%20completed%20what%20Dhoni%20practically%20couldn't.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20momentous%20triumph%20over%20Australia%20in%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20semi-final%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20made%20India%20the%20first%20side%20to%20reach%20the%20fifth%20Champions%20Trophy%20final%2C%20no%20other%20team%20has%20reached%20more%20than%20three.%20Since%20Rohit%20took%20over%20full-time%20captaincy%20in%20February%202022%2C%20India%20has%20toppled%20several%20records.%20In%20a%20span%20of%20three%20years%2C%20India%20has%20entered%20into%20the%20finals%20of%20every%20ICC%20tournament%2C%20making%20him%20the%20first%20skipper%20to%20achieve%20the%20feat.%20An%20unsung%20hero%20who%20is%20rarely%20seen%20being%20cherished%20for%20the%20tactics%20he%20implements%20with%20his%20rich%20cricketing%20brain%2C%20Rohit's%20untouched%20record%20has%20now%20made%20him%20one%20of%20the%20best%20captains%20the%20sport%20has%20ever%20witnessed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Rohit%20at%20the%20helm%2C%20India%20marched%20into%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20final%20in%202023%20but%20succumbed%20to%20a%20209-run%20defeat.%20In%20the%20same%20year%2C%20India%20progressed%20to%20the%20final%20of%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%202023%20unbeaten%20but%20saw%20their%20entire%20campaign%20collapse%20in%20the%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralia%20staged%20a%20heartbreak%20for%20the%20Indian%20team%20and%20its%20fans%20by%20staging%20a%206-wicket%20victory%20in%20Ahmedabad%20to%20lift%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20for%20a%20record%20sixth%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seasoned%20opener%20brushed%20away%20the%20heartbreak%20and%20orchestrated%20a%20record-shattering%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20campaign.%20He%20was%20the%20mastermind%20behind%20India%20going%20all%20the%20way%20to%20Barbados%20to%20lift%20the%20title%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%202007%2C%20that%20too%20without%20savouring%20defeat%20once%20in%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Champions%20Trophy%20was%20the%20only%20tournament%20left%20out%20of%20Rohit's%20grasp%2C%20and%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20he%20made%20history%20in%20Dubai%20by%20leading%20the%20Men%20in%20Blue%20to%20the%20final%20of%20the%20marquee%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20policy%20of%20a%20fearless%20approach%2C%20India%20savoured%20the%20sweet%20taste%20of%20revenge%20by%20punching%20Australia's%20return%20ticket%20home.%20In%20pursuit%20of%20a%20modest%20265-run%20target%2C%20Virat%20Kohli's%20chase%20masterclass%20left%20the%20Baggy%20Greens%20gobsmacked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirat%20choreographed%20a%20flawless%20route%20to%20the%20final%20with%20his%20swashbuckling%2084(98)%2C%20with%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20playing%20second%20fiddle%20with%20his%20invaluable%2045(62).%20By%20executing%20a%20memorable%20chase%2C%20India%20rewrote%20the%20record%20of%20completing%20its%20most%20successful%20run%20chase%20against%20Australia%20in%20an%20ICC%20event%2C%20bettering%20the%20previous%20best%20chase%20of%20261%20in%202011%20World%20Cup%20quarter-final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20ANI%20Inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741141860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F9h03o108_sd_625x300_04_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Frohit-sharma-goes-a-step-ahead-of-ms-dhoni-in-icc-events-becomes-first-captain-ever-to-7848729%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rohit%20Sharma%20shatter