7045-600x800.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-89_11zon-1740397045-450x600.jpg%20450w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-89_11zon-1740397045-300x400.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-89_11zon-1740397045-150x200.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-89_11zon-1740397045.jpg%20620w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-408999%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EArchana%20feels%20blessed%20to%20be%20guided%20by%20her%20mentor%2C%20Shubham%20Pandey%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Shubham%20saw%20the%20potential%20she%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20recognised.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20explained%20my%20natural%20ability%20to%20equalise%20(adjusting%20the%20air%20pressure%20in%20the%20middle%20ear%20to%20the%20water%20pressure%20)%20as%20a%20key%20advantage.%20I%20initially%20hesitated%2C%20wanting%20to%20refine%20my%20skills%2C%20and%20then%20dedicated%20myself%20to%20training%20in%20Indonesia%20and%20the%20Philippines%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShubham%E2%80%99s%20influence%20has%20been%20profound.%20%E2%80%9CHis%20generous%20sharing%20of%20knowledge%2C%20his%20secure%20support%20in%20this%20field%2C%20and%20his%20emphasis%20on%20ocean%20conservation%20over%20competition%20have%20shaped%20my%20approach%20to%20diving%20and%20mentorship%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Archana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20want%20to%20make%20freediving%20accessible%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArchana%E2%80%99s%20vision%20extends%20beyond%20personal%20success.%20She%20is%20actively%20working%20to%20bring%20AIDA%20(International%20Association%20for%20the%20Development%20of%20Apnea)%2C%20the%20international%20freediving%20organisation%